These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-1::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: baking, dancing, hiking, reading, singing
There are 5 different nationalities: brazilian, british, chinese, pakistani, russian
5 different games are played: domino, billiard, go, monopoly, scrabble
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, havana, blend, chaman, siglo
 1. the blend-smoker is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
 2. the siglo-smoker is the person who's hobby is singing##1
 3. the havana-smoker is on the right of the brazilian##1
 4. the davidoff-smoker is on the right of the chinese##1
 5. the person playing billiard is the pakistani##1
 6. the british is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 7. the person playing domino is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
 8. the british is on the far left##1
 9. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the british##1
10. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1
11. the person playing billiard is the davidoff-smoker##1
12. the person playing go is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |    5     |
| Hobby         | dancing  | baking    | reading | hiking    | singing  |
| Nationality   | british  | brazilian | chinese | pakistani | russian  |
| Game           | domino     | scrabble     | monopoly  | billiard   | go    |
| Cigar         | blend | chaman    | havana | davidoff  | siglo |

