.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-2::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: dubstep, pop, house, ambient, funk
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: begonia, rose, iris, marigold, dahlia
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: adventure, animation, documentary, family, martial-arts
There are 5 different nationalities: argentine, indonesian, mexican, russian, spanish
 1. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the argentine##1
 2. the mexican is the person watching animation movies##1
 3. the indonesian is on the right of the russian##1
 4. the person watching documentary movies is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
 6. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
 7. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
 8. the fan of house is the person watching documentary movies##1
 9. the russian is the fan of house##1
10. the fan of pop is in the middle##1
11. the fan of ambient is on the left of the mexican##1
12. the fan of house is the person who growsrose##1
13. the fan of funk is on the left of the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3       |      4       |     5      |
| Music-Genre          | house        | funk | pop     | ambient      | dubstep  |
| Flower           | rose   | iris | dahlia    | marigold | begonia |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | family     | martial-arts | adventure    | animation  |
| Nationality   | russian     | indonesian | argentine    | spanish      | mexican    |

