.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-3::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: fanta, milk, sprite, tea, water
The people have 5 different hobbies: cooking, magic-tricks, reading, traveling, writing
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: action, drama, crime, family, disaster
House: modern, palace, tower, victorian, colonial
 1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
 2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 3. the person watching action movies is in the middle##1
 4. the person drinking milk is in the middle##1
 5. the person watching crime movies is on the far right##1
 6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far left##1
 7. the victorian house is on the right of the palace house##1
 8. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
 9. the colonial house is in the middle##1
10. the tower house is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
11. the person watching crime movies is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
12. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
13. the person drinking tea is the person watching drama movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |     3      |     4     |     5      |
| Beverage      | tea          | sprite  | milk       | fanta     | water      |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | writing | traveling  | reading   | cooking    |
| Movie-Genre   | drama        | disaster | action | family    | crime   |
| House     | modern   | tower | colonial      | palace | victorian |

