 7. the person driving the car is on the right of the prince-smoker##1
 8. the person driving the van is in the middle##1
 9. the fan of pop is on the left of the entrepreneur##1
10. the videographer is the fan of indie##1
11. the manager is on the left of the videographer##1
12. the person driving the bike is on the left of the fan of techno##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |   3    |    4    |     5     |
| Job          | architect        | entrepreneur       | firefighter | manager   | videographer  |
| Cigar   | prince | dunhill | game | dannemann   | vegafina |
| Music-Genre   | pop         | techno     | gospel | country | indie     |
| Transport     | bike        | car        | van    | taxi    | ship      |

