 4. the person eating potato is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
 5. the french is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
 6. the designer is the thai##1
 7. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the photographer##1
 8. the person who growspoppy is in the middle##1
 9. the person eating cauliflower is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
10. the person eating potato is on the far right##1
11. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
12. the polish is on the left of the person eating potato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |      4       |      5      |
