.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-8::.
5 different games are played: monopoly, go, poker, snooker, backgammon
There are 5 different nationalities: american, egyptian, german, nigerian, turkish
5 different pets are kept: chinchilla, ferret, goldfish, hamster, snake
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: august, october, june, january, april
 1. the person who's birthday is in august is the person playing monopoly##1
 2. the person playing go is on the right of the american##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far left##1
 4. the german is on the right of the nigerian##1
 5. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person playing poker##1
 6. the person playing poker is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
 7. the owner of the hamster is on the far right##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person playing go##1
 9. the german is the person who's birthday is in june##1
10. the turkish is in the middle##1
11. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the turkish##1
12. the owner of the snake is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
13. the person playing poker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
14. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3    |       4       |    5     |
| Game      | monopoly        | snooker   | go  | poker         | backgammon |
| Nationality   | egyptian   | american   | turkish | nigerian      | german   |
| Pet           | chinchilla | goldfish   | snake   | ferret        | hamster  |
| Birthday         | august   | october | january | april | june  |

