 3. the person playing go is on the right of the fan of country##1
 4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person playing canasta##1
 5. the fan of r&b is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 6. the person playing canasta is the fan of electronic##1
 7. the person who's sport is soccer is the fan of electronic##1
 8. the person playing go is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 9. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far left##1
10. the person playing backgammon is the person who's sport is swimming##1
11. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the fan of folk##1
12. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
13. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
