.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-17::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, cola, iced-tea, juice, milk
5 different games are played: chess, canasta, monopoly, poker, bridge
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: blues, country, folk, house, reggae
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: begonia, sunflower, dahlia, zinnia, tulip
 1. the person playing canasta is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
 2. the person drinking 7up is on the far left##1
 3. the person playing poker is on the left of the fan of blues##1
 4. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the fan of country##1
 5. the person playing chess is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
 6. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
 7. the person playing canasta is the person who growsbegonia##1
 8. the fan of blues is on the left of the person playing chess##1
 9. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
10. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
11. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
12. the person playing monopoly is the fan of house##1
13. the person playing bridge is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |      3       |   4    |    5     |
| Beverage      | 7up      | cola       | milk         | juice  | iced-tea |
| Game   | monopoly  | poker | canasta | chess  | bridge  |
| Music-Genre   | house    | country    | blues        | reggae | folk     |
| Flower           | sunflower | dahlia      | begonia       | zinnia   | tulip   |

