.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-18::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, hot-chocolate, milk, lemonade, 7up
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: blues, country, folk, gospel, jazz
House: farmhouse, palace, ranch-style, gothic-revival, futuristic
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: basketball, rowing, sailing, swimming, volleyball
 1. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the futuristic house##1
 2. the fan of folk is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 3. the ranch-style house is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 4. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 5. the futuristic house is on the left of the fan of folk##1
 6. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
 7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person who's sport is basketball##1
 8. the person drinking milk is the fan of country##1
 9. the palace house is in the middle##1
10. the farmhouse house is the fan of jazz##1
11. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
12. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
13. the person drinking lemonade is the fan of jazz##1

