.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-19::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, lemonade, milk, tea
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: may, february, march, june, august
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: climbing, cricket, soccer, rowing, volleyball
The people use 5 different means of transport: car, jet-ski, roller, ship, tram
 1. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
 2. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in august is the person driving the car##1
 4. the person driving the roller is on the far right##1
 5. the person driving the jet-ski is the person drinking lemonade##1
 6. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
 7. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 8. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the car##1
 9. the person driving the car is in the middle##1
10. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
11. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
12. the person who's birthday is in march is the person drinking tea##1
13. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
