.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-20::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: superhero, mystery, documentary, animation, horror
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: blues, country, pop, punk, salsa
There are 5 different nationalities: argentine, british, italian, polish, thai
5 different pets are kept: goldfish, ferret, mouse, bird, rat
 1. the person watching documentary movies is in the middle##1
 2. the fan of punk is the owner of the goldfish##1
 3. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the fan of punk##1
 4. the fan of blues is the thai##1
 5. the owner of the rat is on the far right##1
 6. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
 7. the fan of pop is the british##1
 8. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
 9. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
10. the person watching mystery movies is on the far left##1
11. the fan of blues is on the far right##1
12. the fan of salsa is in the middle##1
13. the argentine is the person watching animation movies##1
14. the polish is on the left of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |    3    |     4      |   5    |
| Movie-Genre      | mystery | animation   | documentary    | superhero       | horror |
| Music-Genre   | pop           | country   | salsa   | punk       | blues  |
| Nationality   | british       | argentine | italian | polish     | thai   |
| Pet     | mouse    | ferret   | bird   | goldfish | rat   |

 